{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"When I was a kid, I was obsessed\nwith the Guinness Book of World Records,"},{"time":5320,"text":"and I really wanted\nto set a world record myself."},{"time":8800,"text":"But there was just one small problem:"},{"time":11520,"text":"I had absolutely no talent."},{"time":14520,"text":"So I decided to set\na world record in something"},{"time":17960,"text":"that demanded absolutely no skill at all."},{"time":21840,"text":"I decided to set a world record"},{"time":24600,"text":"in crawling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30680,"text":"Now, the record at the time\nwas 12 and a half miles,"},{"time":35840,"text":"and for some reason,\nthis seemed totally manageable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":42640,"text":"I recruited my friend Anne,"},{"time":44160,"text":"and together we decided,\nwe didn't even need to train."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51040,"text":"And on the day of our record attempt,"},{"time":52880,"text":"we put furniture pads\non the outside of our good luck jeans"},{"time":56560,"text":"and we set off,"},{"time":58720,"text":"and right away, we were in trouble,"},{"time":61800,"text":"because the denim was against our skin"},{"time":63920,"text":"and it began to chafe,"},{"time":65519,"text":"and soon our knees were being chewed up."},{"time":68920,"text":"Hours in,"},{"time":71160,"text":"it began to rain."},{"time":73520,"text":"Then, Anne dropped out."},{"time":77400,"text":"Then, it got dark."},{"time":80680,"text":"Now, by now, my knees\nwere bleeding through my jeans,"},{"time":83520,"text":"and I was hallucinating from the cold"},{"time":85760,"text":"and the pain and the monotony."},{"time":88480,"text":"And to give you an idea\nof the suffer-fest that I was undergoing,"},{"time":93120,"text":"the first lap around\nthe high school track took 10 minutes."},{"time":97880,"text":"The last lap took almost 30."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"After 12 hours of crawling,"},{"time":106440,"text":"I stopped,"},{"time":107800,"text":"and I had gone eight and a half miles."},{"time":111880,"text":"So I was short of\nthe 12-and-a-half-mile record."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115560,"text":"Now, for many years, I thought\nthis was a story of abject failure,"},{"time":120120,"text":"but today I see it differently,"},{"time":122640,"text":"because when I was\nattempting the world record,"},{"time":125520,"text":"I was doing three things."},{"time":127040,"text":"I was getting outside my comfort zone,"},{"time":129400,"text":"I was calling upon my resilience,"},{"time":131680,"text":"and I was finding confidence in myself"},{"time":134440,"text":"and my own decisions."},{"time":136440,"text":"I didn't know it then,"},{"time":137720,"text":"but those are not\nthe attributes of failure."},{"time":141480,"text":"Those are the attributes of bravery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145280,"text":"Now, in 1989, at the age of 26,"},{"time":147880,"text":"I became a San Francisco firefighter,"},{"time":150800,"text":"and I was the 15th woman\nin a department of 1,500 men."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":161240,"text":"And as you can imagine, when I arrived"},{"time":163120,"text":"there were many doubts\nabout whether we could do the job."},{"time":165840,"text":"So even though I was a 5'10\",\n150-pound collegiate rower,"},{"time":171200,"text":"and someone who could endure\n12 hours of searing knee pain --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":175600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177240,"text":"I knew I still had to prove\nmy strength and fitness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180280,"text":"So one day a call came in for a fire,"},{"time":182120,"text":"and sure enough,\nwhen my engine group pulled up,"},{"time":184383,"text":"there was black smoke billowing\nfrom a building off an alleyway."},{"time":188440,"text":"And I was with a big guy named Skip,"},{"time":190680,"text":"and he was on the nozzle,\nand I was right behind,"},{"time":193440,"text":"and it was a typical sort of fire."},{"time":195280,"text":"It was smoky, it was hot,"},{"time":198680,"text":"and all of a sudden,"},{"time":200400,"text":"there was an explosion,"},{"time":202200,"text":"and Skip and I were blown backwards,"},{"time":204400,"text":"my mask was knocked sideways,"},{"time":206560,"text":"and there was this moment of confusion."},{"time":208840,"text":"And then I picked myself up,"},{"time":212280,"text":"I groped for the nozzle,"},{"time":214120,"text":"and I did what a firefighter\nwas supposed to do:"},{"time":216640,"text":"I lunged forward,"},{"time":218400,"text":"opened up the water"},{"time":219880,"text":"and I tackled the fire myself."},{"time":222720,"text":"The explosion had been caused\nby a water heater,"},{"time":225000,"text":"so nobody was hurt,\nand ultimately it was not a big deal,"},{"time":227720,"text":"but later Skip came up to me and said,"},{"time":231000,"text":"\"Nice job, Caroline,\""},{"time":232760,"text":"in this surprised sort of voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":237600,"text":"And I was confused, because\nthe fire hadn't been difficult physically,"},{"time":241440,"text":"so why was he looking at me\nwith something like astonishment?"},{"time":246480,"text":"And then it became clear:"},{"time":248160,"text":"Skip, who was by the way a really nice guy"},{"time":251320,"text":"and an excellent firefighter,"},{"time":253560,"text":"not only thought\nthat women could not be strong,"},{"time":256959,"text":"he thought that they\ncould not be brave either."},{"time":260760,"text":"And he wasn't the only one."},{"time":263560,"text":"Friends, acquaintances and strangers,"},{"time":265840,"text":"men and women throughout my career"},{"time":267920,"text":"ask me over and over,"},{"time":269400,"text":"\"Caroline, all that fire, all that danger,"},{"time":273360,"text":"aren't you scared?\""},{"time":275320,"text":"Honestly, I never heard\na male firefighter asked this."},{"time":278920,"text":"And I became curious."},{"time":281200,"text":"Why wasn't bravery expected of women?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":285760,"text":"Now, the answer began to come"},{"time":287560,"text":"when a friend of mine lamented to me"},{"time":289320,"text":"that her young daughter\nwas a big scaredy-cat,"},{"time":291800,"text":"and so I began to notice,"},{"time":293760,"text":"and yes, the daughter was anxious,"},{"time":296480,"text":"but more than that,\nthe parents were anxious."},{"time":300120,"text":"Most of what they said to her\nwhen she was outside began with,"},{"time":303400,"text":"\"Be careful,\" \"Watch out,\" or \"No.\""},{"time":308920,"text":"Now, my friends were not bad parents."},{"time":311600,"text":"They were just doing what most parents do,"},{"time":314320,"text":"which is cautioning their daughters\nmuch more than they caution their sons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319440,"text":"There was a study involving\na playground fire pole, ironically,"},{"time":324480,"text":"in which researchers saw that little girls\nwere very likely to be warned"},{"time":328600,"text":"by both their moms and dads\nabout the fire pole's risk,"},{"time":332320,"text":"and if the little girls\nstill wanted to play on the fire pole,"},{"time":335800,"text":"a parent was very likely to assist her."},{"time":339280,"text":"But the little boys?"},{"time":341160,"text":"They were encouraged\nto play on the fire pole"},{"time":343960,"text":"despite any trepidations\nthat they might have,"},{"time":346920,"text":"and often the parents offered\nguidance on how to use it on their own."},{"time":353480,"text":"So what message does this send\nto both boys and girls?"},{"time":357920,"text":"Well, that girls are fragile\nand more in need of help,"},{"time":361880,"text":"and that boys can and should\nmaster difficult tasks by themselves."},{"time":366520,"text":"It says that girls should be fearful"},{"time":369280,"text":"and boys should be gutsy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373160,"text":"Now, the irony is that at this young age,"},{"time":375680,"text":"girls and boys are actually\nvery alike physically."},{"time":378200,"text":"In fact, girls are often\nstronger until puberty,"},{"time":380880,"text":"and more mature."},{"time":382480,"text":"And yet we adults act"},{"time":384480,"text":"as if girls are more fragile"},{"time":386840,"text":"and more in need of help,"},{"time":388800,"text":"and they can't handle as much."},{"time":391160,"text":"This is the message\nthat we absorb as kids,"},{"time":393760,"text":"and this is the message\nthat fully permeates as we grow up."},{"time":397480,"text":"We women believe it, men believe it,"},{"time":399960,"text":"and guess what?"},{"time":401520,"text":"As we become parents,\nwe pass it on to our children,"},{"time":404880,"text":"and so it goes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406720,"text":"Well, so now I had my answer."},{"time":409240,"text":"This is why women, even firewomen,"},{"time":411840,"text":"were expected to be scared."},{"time":413960,"text":"This is why women often are scared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417920,"text":"Now, I know some of you\nwon't believe me when I tell you this,"},{"time":421080,"text":"but I am not against fear."},{"time":424200,"text":"I know it's an important emotion,\nand it's there to keep us safe."},{"time":428040,"text":"But the problem is\nwhen fear is the primary reaction"},{"time":431240,"text":"that we teach and encourage in girls"},{"time":433600,"text":"whenever they face something\noutside their comfort zone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437760,"text":"So I was a paraglider pilot\nfor many years --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":441800,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":443720,"text":"and a paraglider is a parachute-like wing,"},{"time":446160,"text":"and it does fly very well,"},{"time":449920,"text":"but to many people I realize\nit looks just like a bedsheet"},{"time":452840,"text":"with strings attached."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":455560,"text":"And I spent a lot of time on mountaintops"},{"time":458040,"text":"inflating this bedsheet,"},{"time":459640,"text":"running off and flying."},{"time":462560,"text":"And I know what you're thinking."},{"time":464160,"text":"You're like, Caroline,\na little fear would make sense here."},{"time":468800,"text":"And you're right, it does."},{"time":470680,"text":"I assure you, I did feel fear."},{"time":473200,"text":"But on that mountaintop,"},{"time":474480,"text":"waiting for the wind\nto come in just right,"},{"time":476560,"text":"I felt so many other things, too:"},{"time":478800,"text":"exhilaration, confidence."},{"time":482000,"text":"I knew I was a good pilot."},{"time":483800,"text":"I knew the conditions were good,\nor I wouldn't be there."},{"time":486840,"text":"I knew how great it was going to be\na thousand feet in the air."},{"time":490400,"text":"So yes, fear was there,"},{"time":493040,"text":"but I would take a good hard look at it,"},{"time":495240,"text":"assess just how relevant it was"},{"time":497920,"text":"and then put it where it belonged,"},{"time":500280,"text":"which was more often than not"},{"time":501720,"text":"behind my exhilaration, my anticipation"},{"time":505720,"text":"and my confidence."},{"time":507400,"text":"So I'm not against fear."},{"time":509440,"text":"I'm just pro-bravery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":514520,"text":"Now, I'm not saying\nyour girls must be firefighters"},{"time":517760,"text":"or that they should be paragliders,"},{"time":520000,"text":"but I am saying that we are raising\nour girls to be timid, even helpless,"},{"time":525600,"text":"and it begins when we caution them\nagainst physical risk."},{"time":529240,"text":"The fear we learn\nand the experiences we don't"},{"time":531880,"text":"stay with us as we become women"},{"time":533720,"text":"and morphs into all those things\nthat we face and try to shed:"},{"time":538000,"text":"our hesitation in speaking out,"},{"time":540320,"text":"our deference so that we can be liked"},{"time":543000,"text":"and our lack of confidence\nin our own decisions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546960,"text":"So how do we become brave?"},{"time":550440,"text":"Well, here's the good news."},{"time":552240,"text":"Bravery is learned,"},{"time":554240,"text":"and like anything learned,"},{"time":555680,"text":"it just needs to be practiced."},{"time":558040,"text":"So first,"},{"time":559640,"text":"we have to take a deep breath"},{"time":561360,"text":"and encourage our girls"},{"time":563440,"text":"to skateboard, climb trees"},{"time":566160,"text":"and clamber around\non that playground fire pole."},{"time":569480,"text":"This is what my own mother did."},{"time":571680,"text":"She didn't know it then,"},{"time":573480,"text":"but researchers have a name for this."},{"time":575800,"text":"They call it risky play,"},{"time":577920,"text":"and studies show that risky play\nis really important for kids, all kids,"},{"time":582400,"text":"because it teaches hazard assessment,"},{"time":585000,"text":"it teaches delayed gratification,"},{"time":587200,"text":"it teaches resilience,"},{"time":589000,"text":"it teaches confidence."},{"time":591080,"text":"In other words,"},{"time":592560,"text":"when kids get outside\nand practice bravery,"},{"time":595880,"text":"they learn valuable life lessons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600600,"text":"Second, we have to stop\ncautioning our girls willy-nilly."},{"time":605360,"text":"So notice next time you say,"},{"time":607800,"text":"\"Watch out, you're going to get hurt,\""},{"time":609680,"text":"or, \"Don't do that, it's dangerous.\""},{"time":612480,"text":"And remember that often\nwhat you're really telling her"},{"time":616080,"text":"is that she shouldn't be pushing herself,"},{"time":618520,"text":"that she's really not good enough,"},{"time":620720,"text":"that she should be afraid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624320,"text":"Third,"},{"time":626080,"text":"we women have to start\npracticing bravery, too."},{"time":629880,"text":"We cannot teach our girls\nuntil we teach ourselves."},{"time":633960,"text":"So here's another thing:"},{"time":635880,"text":"fear and exhilaration"},{"time":639000,"text":"feel very similar --"},{"time":641760,"text":"the shaky hands,\nthe heightened heart rate,"},{"time":644360,"text":"the nervous tension,"},{"time":645760,"text":"and I'm betting that for many of you"},{"time":647520,"text":"the last time you thought\nyou were scared out of your wits,"},{"time":650360,"text":"you may have been feeling\nmostly exhilaration,"},{"time":653320,"text":"and now you've missed an opportunity."},{"time":655720,"text":"So practice."},{"time":657560,"text":"And while girls should be getting\noutside to learn to be gutsy,"},{"time":660560,"text":"I get that adults don't want\nto get on hoverboards or climb trees,"},{"time":666680,"text":"so we all should be practicing"},{"time":670160,"text":"at home, in the office"},{"time":672400,"text":"and even right here getting up the guts"},{"time":674520,"text":"to talk to someone that you really admire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":678360,"text":"Finally, when your girl is, let's say,"},{"time":682400,"text":"on her bike on the top of the steep hill"},{"time":684520,"text":"that she insists\nshe's too scared to go down,"},{"time":687960,"text":"guide her to access her bravery."},{"time":690720,"text":"Ultimately, maybe that hill\nreally is too steep,"},{"time":695000,"text":"but she'll come to that conclusion\nthrough courage, not fear."},{"time":699920,"text":"Because this is not\nabout the steep hill in front of her."},{"time":703840,"text":"This is about the life ahead of her"},{"time":706400,"text":"and that she has the tools"},{"time":708200,"text":"to handle and assess"},{"time":710320,"text":"all the dangers\nthat we cannot protect her from,"},{"time":713600,"text":"all the challenges that we won't\nbe there to guide her through,"},{"time":718160,"text":"everything that our girls here"},{"time":720640,"text":"and around the world"},{"time":722040,"text":"face in their future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726200,"text":"So by the way,"},{"time":728400,"text":"the world record for crawling today --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":731200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":733600,"text":"is 35.18 miles,"},{"time":738520,"text":"and I would really love\nto see a girl go break that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}